{"tid":1555744,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"幾時搞一次集會or遊行聲援新屋嶺班手足搞大佢！","createTime":"2019-09-09T12:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T14:23:19.000Z","uid":217242,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1607ef121c0588c4f62d69dfc09555c9355a212b","tid":1555744,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:50:45.000Z","msg":"因為831放狗落站咬人同無交代CCTV<br />\n我地都表示憤怒不能夠接受<br />\n但係新屋嶺入邊係直程<span style=\"color: gold;\">無Cam</span><br />\n入邊班手足又會受到如何<span style=\"color: red;\">不人道對待</span>？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n831我明白大家都好嬲 包括我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且整件事係非常疑點重重<br />\n但係831事件後到依家<br />\n我地對警察同黨鐵好似都係無關痛癢咁<br />\n另外我地亦唔排除有831手足捉咗去新屋嶺<br />\n<br />\n其實我想講除咗831之外<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">新屋嶺都係非常嚴重嘅一件大事！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入邊係無cam架！<br />\n基本上做乜都得！</span></span><br />\n而我之前睇到有新聞話被捕人士<br />\n正常應該係要留係當區警署羈留室<br />\n<br />\n所以我地係唔係好應該為個1000幾位手足聲援<br />\n我唔係話831當日手足唔重要<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係我地<span style=\"color: gold;\">懷疑</span>831之餘<br />\n亦同時唔能夠<span style=\"color: gold;\">習慣</span>新屋嶺處理手法</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我其實講咁大段廢話<br />\n都係想問大家<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幾時行動升級呀！</span></span><br />\n我地仲要守到幾時？！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人可以一齊探討一下日後點做<br />\n上星期五六日已經有157個手足市民被拘捕<br />\n我地仲要維持呢個現象到幾時？<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每一次都係大家出去</span><br />\n跟住被拘捕 然後唔滿意出去 又被拘捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而對家完全一副你吹我唔漲咁嘅態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/crzegMh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcrzegMh.gif&h=e66e4515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上純粹發開口夢亂講 <br />\n如日後屬實 純屬意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc7907d16485dbfb78c86ff284200f401cfa8eb","tid":1555744,"uid":67232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:51:41.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n914天水圍、915民陣大遊行"},{"pid":"859d84fcc32699d0ac259fc9c729d63d9dfc91f5","tid":1555744,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:54:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc26db354589066e82eff2f561146cac7609ed9","tid":1555744,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f82581e40734c109a168ff4d31a5f855498f3a","tid":1555744,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:54:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cbad78f0c25e1f1b77bdbe6679c313c7f30d1d8","tid":1555744,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0907d48d074b33f7c4cdd1e192a0a1a601f3f295","tid":1555744,"uid":43936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:55:37.000Z","msg":"YES TUI!<br />\n612 721 811 831"},{"pid":"71ade074eeb0f821935cbbe27a27b7f83fac13df","tid":1555744,"uid":311337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:55:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99dbcd5d700a15f38f54d6301b7d1c9c5eb1755e","tid":1555744,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci